  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\"><img alt=\"House Shett of Gulltown.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/50px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/75px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/100px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Uther Shett</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\"><img alt=\"House Shett of Gulltown.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/50px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/75px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg/100px-House_Shett_of_Gulltown.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\">House Shett of Gulltown</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/281_AC\" title=\"281 AC\">281</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/285_AC\" title=\"285 AC\">285&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Uther Shett</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> and a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Shett_of_Gulltown\" title=\"House Shett of Gulltown\">House Shett of Gulltown</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Uther_Shett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Uther is a skinny, ginger-haired young man no more than eighteen years old. His face is covered in pimples, which he attempts to hide behind his whiskers.<sup id=\"cite_ref-alayneI_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-alayneI-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Uther_Shett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Uther_Shett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Uther Shett arrives at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a> to compete in Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert Arryn</a>'s tourney for a place in the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_of_Winged_Knights\" title=\"Brotherhood of Winged Knights\">Brotherhood of Winged Knights</a>. While flirting with <a href=\"/index.php/Myranda_Royce\" title=\"Myranda Royce\">Myranda Royce</a> along Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ossifer_Lipps\" title=\"Ossifer Lipps\">Ossifer Lipps</a>, he is interrupted by <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Alayne Stone</a>, who rescues Myranda from their unwanted advances. During the feast on the eve of the tourney, Uther treads upon Alayne's feet when the two dances.<sup id=\"cite_ref-alayneI_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-alayneI-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Uther_Shett&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages_(Continued3)#Uther_Shett\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages (Continued3)\">Uther Shett</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-alayneI-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-alayneI_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-alayneI_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_I_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Alayne I (The Winds of Winter)\">Alayne I</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403100424\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds